<p>Prof Anita Ghosh, former board member of ASFAA, passed away with her sincere devotion and contribution remained with us.  </p><p>She was also the president of All India Association of Sport for All, follower of TAFISA and a pioneer of sport for all in India. She put great effort into promoting Sports for All during her life time, announced valuable researches and made speeches in international congresses. </p><p>We are not only grieved at the passing of a tremendous individual but also for the loss in the field of sport for all. Our thoughts are with her family at this sad time.</p>